Britvic Plans Global Expansion Through Franchising, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-14T03:23:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/britvic-plans-global-expansion-through-franchising-ft-reports.html
  Britvic Plc (BVIC)  is planning
international expansion through global franchising and has
launched pilot projects in  Australia  and in the U.S. southeast,
Chief Financial Officer John Gibney said at a conference in
Edinburgh, the Financial Times reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
